      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MY ERNIE JAY (3) has been hard to follow lately, running fifth (22.99) last time but prior to that ran very well when placed at Q Straight. Expecting significant improvement this line-up. HOWDY ROSE (2) has been beaten for early speed lately, last time finishing eighth (22.82) in a Grade 3/4 at this track. Has a good record here at this journey. Will give the top chances plenty to think about. MAIN WAY (1) turned in a better run last time to find a minor placing (22.29) at this track behind Don't Cry Mama in a Mix 5. Has the early speed to land on the pace and can stick on. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings four times from seven starts. Expected to be in the finish again. OAK'S BEST (4) has ability and can feature with the right run after missing a cheque here most recently.",
